{"tid":1472214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如LIHKG 以後只可以開一個集中討論PO 做反思, 檢討","createTime":"2019-08-14T13:29:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T07:50:18.000Z","uid":294,"like":38,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"d17aabfd63f446cf4de8b5c819ca894943515abd","tid":1472214,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:29:15.000Z","msg":"知道前線唔係完美, 意見都唔一定完美<br />\n但不斷開PO 只會自己人打自己人, <br />\nLIHKG 以後只可以開一個集中討論PO 做反思, 檢討<br />\n以防五毛扮和理非不斷開PO 帶風向<br />\n<br />\n如果發現有人私下開割席前線PO<br />\n既report 洗版, 個po 移去黑洞<br />\n多次發現即禁言1個月<br />\n<br />\n總之live 示威期間, 嚴禁私下開po 屌示威者"},{"pid":"9a4a2611b9806a7bf0c47a95756184bfeabed41d","tid":1472214,"uid":34063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:29:47.000Z","msg":"對於圍機場，我有啲野講<br />\n- <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dEwHdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dEwHdS</a><br />\n<br />\n推, 並說著<br />\n612, 721, 811<br />\n光復香港, 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求, 缺一不可<br />\n不受傷 不被捕 不抹黑<br />\n不分化 不篤灰 不割蓆<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">接下來重點活動：</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TmWGGaz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTmWGGaz.png&h=e225f9e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wogkrpg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWogkrpg.jpg&h=c9f571c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c88473e6daeaef81454b69d16a69197cacc6abe3","tid":1472214,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:29:52.000Z","msg":"留言等d 扮黃絲五毛話此舉惡過共產黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你可以去集中討論區講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f783e72d9af666783f0dfe2c46ff58da52609725","tid":1472214,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedB